headline: Munchs restaurant, say it aint so! | Letters
sentences: Im still grieving over the closure of Coney Island Grill, where one could inhale hot, juicy, old school, human-scale burgers with high-octane Coca Cola and chili dogs.
Losing access to Munchs Friday Catfish Sandwich, corned beef hash breakfasts or special Wednesday hotcakes would be a gastronomic and communal heartbreaker.

A gastronomic double whammy
I fear news that Munchs restaurant is up for sale might be a double whammy on great comfort food cum sassy wait staff.

Bernard Leikind, Carrollwood
Freedom from carnage
Republican legislators want you to throw up your hands and accept this as a normal way to live.
I recently visited the Magic Kingdom, and aside from some actors dressed as cartoon and movie characters, the only people I saw were families.
But we wont be free until this scourge of violence ends, and we wont stop pressuring its enablers for change until they help end it.

DeSantis, pay attention to the words the dolls will sing:
Its a world of laughter, a world of tears.
Ron DeSantis says that Disney has abandoned its family-friendly attitudes.
They were welcomed by the park staff, and all were having a great time.
Your children will love the gentle boat ride and the singling dolls.
Governor, take your wife and little ones to see for yourself.

Gary Harrington, St. Petersburg
Its a small world
Gov.
Theres so much that we share that its time were aware.
I recommend a visit to the Its a Small World ride.
I think the governor needs to get out more.
Its a world of hopes and a world of fears.
There is just one moon and one golden sun.
And a smile means friendship to everyone.
Though the mountains divide.
Its a small world after all.
Paul Bacon, Hallandale Beach
Its a small world after all.
And the oceans are wide.
The price of freedom.
Gov.
